'''"Elmayı top top yapalım"''' ("Let's do lumps of apples") is a Turkish folk tune.<ref>{{cite web|title=Yöresi|url=https://hbogm.meb.gov.tr/modulerprogramlar/programlar/muzik_gosteri/T%C3%BCrkHalkOyunlari/THO_SakaryaYoresiKadinOyunlari.pdf|format=PDF|website=Hbogm.meb.gov.tr|accessdate=18 March 2017}}</ref> The meter is {{music|time|4|4}}.<ref>{{cite web|title=Elmayı top top yapalım|url=http://www.turkuler.com/nota/ezgi_elmayi_top_top_yapalim.html|website=Turkuler.com|accessdate=18 March 2017}}</ref> The tune is a kind of [[Kaşık Havası]], or spoon dance, the original form of which was popular in [[Hendek]]. Popular recordings include the version by [[Ömer Şan]] & [[Elvan Erbaşı]].

