{{italic title}} {{Use dmy dates|date=September 2016}} '''''Magazyn Wileński''''' (meaning ''Vilnius Journal'' in English) is a [[Polish-language]] monthly political and cultural magazine based in [[Lithuania]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Lithuanian newspapers and magazines|url=http://www.pecob.eu/flex/cm/pages/ServeBLOB.php/L/EN/IDPagina/1371|work=Pecob|accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref> In 2005 it was one of four Polish-language print publications in the country.<ref>{{cite journal|author=Jan Andrlík|title=Ethnic and Language Policy of the Republic of Lithuania: Basis and Practice|journal=Vedeckecasopisy|date=2009|url=http://alppi.vedeckecasopisy.cz/publicFiles/00148.pdf|accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>
